Message.Causes:
The concurrent value change is due to an undesired signal change sequence in a program. Multiple changes of I/O signal might appear when a I/O signal is pulsed, e.g.
SetDO , 0;
PulseDO /High /PLength = 0.01, ;
WaitTime 0.01;
SetDO , 1;
The I/O signal will be 1 at the end, but at rare occasions there will not be any visible pulse. This type of sequence should be avoided.
